<br>
That being said, I've never seen so much reactionary right-wing propganda bullshit in one place since Newt Gingrich lost weight.<br>
<br>
As much as I enjoy endlessly arguing points with people, this is something on which we will never agree. And the next time someone calls me a &quot;pinko commy unamerican xenophobic uncaring asshole loser wasteoid&quot; A) because I happen to have long hair and B) am not for a war that seems to me to be more about finishing what daddy started than it is about terrorism, national security, or weapons of mass destruction, I am going to go off like a SCUD missile. You can either engage in name-calling or you can try to prove a point. You can't do both, especially in the same post. Decide what you want to do, find information to back up your otherwise baseless opinions, and then come back.<br>
